lthBeauty-Instyle-ImageD.jpg 75w,\n/static/1ed72c0d2b0a164abf73aec0e7140b69/4934c/HealthBeauty-Instyle-ImageD.jpg 150w,\n/static/1ed72c0d2b0a164abf73aec0e7140b69/37e03/HealthBeauty-Instyle-ImageD.jpg 300w,\n/static/1ed72c0d2b0a164abf73aec0e7140b69/12ba2/HealthBeauty-Instyle-ImageD.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"/static/1ed72c0d2b0a164abf73aec0e7140b69/ab49a/HealthBeauty-Instyle-ImageD.jpg 75w,\n/static/1ed72c0d2b0a164abf73aec0e7140b69/4934c/HealthBeauty-Instyle-ImageD.jpg 150w,\n/static/1ed72c0d2b0a164abf73aec0e7140b69/37e03/HealthBeauty-Instyle-ImageD.jpg 300w,\n/static/1ed72c0d2b0a164abf73aec0e7140b69/12ba2/HealthBeauty-Instyle-ImageD.jpg 450w\" src=\"/static/1ed72c0d2b0a164abf73aec0e7140b69/37e03/HealthBeauty-Instyle-ImageD.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Surprisingly, you don’t need to reinvent the wheel. Many of these images already exist on your social pages, website, or banner ads, and can be repurposed for native ads that grab consumer attention.</span></p>\n<h4><b>2. Make ads adaptable to a variety of formats. </b></h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Consumers go from desktop to mobile constantly, and that only grows during the holiday season:</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://triplelift.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Holiday-Stats-V2.jpg\"><span class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2811 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:700px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:60.57142857142857%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/d96e8ac6b038ec43e78599592448dbb7/71299/Holiday-Stats-V2-1024x620.jpg 175w,\n/static/d96e8ac6b038ec43e78599592448dbb7/1e9fe/Holiday-Stats-V2-1024x620.jpg 350w,\n/static/d96e8ac6b038ec43e78599592448dbb7/03346/Holiday-Stats-V2-1024x620.jpg 700w,\n/static/d96e8ac6b038ec43e78599592448dbb7/87945/Holiday-Stats-V2-1024x620.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcSet=\"/static/d96e8ac6b038ec43e78599592448dbb7/71299/Holiday-Stats-V2-1024x620.jpg 175w,\n/static/d96e8ac6b038ec43e78599592448dbb7/1e9fe/Holiday-Stats-V2-1024x620.jpg 350w,\n/static/d96e8ac6b038ec43e78599592448dbb7/03346/Holiday-Stats-V2-1024x620.jpg 700w,\n/static/d96e8ac6b038ec43e78599592448dbb7/87945/Holiday-Stats-V2-1024x620.jpg 1024w\" src=\"/static/d96e8ac6b038ec43e78599592448dbb7/03346/Holiday-Stats-V2-1024x620.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/d96e8ac6b038ec43e78599592448dbb7/71299/Holiday-Stats-V2-1024x620.jpg 175w,\n/static/d96e8ac6b038ec43e78599592448dbb7/1e9fe/Holiday-Stats-V2-1024x620.jpg 350w,\n/static/d96e8ac6b038ec43e78599592448dbb7/03346/Holiday-Stats-V2-1024x620.jpg 700w,\n/static/d96e8ac6b038ec43e78599592448dbb7/87945/Holiday-Stats-V2-1024x620.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"/static/d96e8ac6b038ec43e78599592448dbb7/71299/Holiday-Stats-V2-1024x620.jpg 175w,\n/static/d96e8ac6b038ec43e78599592448dbb7/1e9fe/Holiday-Stats-V2-1024x620.jpg 350w,\n/static/d96e8ac6b038ec43e78599592448dbb7/03346/Holiday-Stats-V2-1024x620.jpg 700w,\n/static/d96e8ac6b038ec43e78599592448dbb7/87945/Holiday-Stats-V2-1024x620.jpg 1024w\" src=\"/static/d96e8ac6b038ec43e78599592448dbb7/03346/Holiday-Stats-V2-1024x620.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Your native ads should display well on not only desktop, but also on the variety of mobile display opportunities that consumers indulge in. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This can be done programmatically with TripleLift’s platform, which adapts your assets automatically (leveraging computer vision), so the most important pieces of your ads are always in frame — no matter how the dimensions change.</span></p>\n<h4><b>3. Target your creative for different audiences. </b></h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The best ads speak directly to the needs and wants of your consumer. Your brand caters to any number of personas, so it’s important that your creative reflect their individuality. As you set your programmatic strategy, remember to tweak ads for the various audiences you want to target, with creative that puts each of their needs at the forefront.</span></p>\n<h4></h4>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Start creating high-quality assets now for your holiday advertising campaigns.&nbsp;</strong></h5>\n<p><a href=\"https://triplelift.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/HolidayBestPractices-GetStarted.jpg\"><span class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2799 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:800px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:60.5%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/ae383aa919457000f1500ecd624d48d6/16d62/HolidayBestPractices-GetStarted-1024x620.jpg 200w,\n/static/ae38